# repos.manifest — the services that make up the system, and the shared slice branch.
#
# ACTIVE_BRANCH  <branch>          the branch every repo sits on for the current vertical slice
# <name>  <remote-url>             one line per service repo
#
# Edit ACTIVE_BRANCH via `./scripts/sync-branches.sh <branch>` (it rewrites this line), not by hand.

